reviewText: two awesome movies - fast shipping
saw these movies before and wanted to add them to collection.
I am very happy with the videos. They came in quick and the disk are in perfect condition. I am very happy with the product.
Again an easy transaction and product was exactly as described.  Amazon has once again made life easier to enjoy without fighting the crowds.

Sean Penn goes after gang members in Los Angeles, then has to deal with his nutty father in crime-ridden rural Nebraska (Christopher Walken) in the sequel. Oh, snap! These movies are totally awesome. Sean Penn is a fine actor. Christopher Penn is in one of them, too, before he was fat. And dead.

colors was very good a lot of action & heart felt moments just a good  movie.

At Close Range was  also very good Sean Penn his brother Chris Penn and his their mother Eilene Ryan.

it was a treat seeing how family could work so well with each other an  not miss a beat in making a fantastic movie. it was a movie you could watch over and over and I have many times.
A GREAT deal on 2 movies together. You just about CANNOT go wrong with a Robert Duvall OR a Chris Walken movie EVER!  But,if ANYTHING,it COULD use MORE "Cow Bell"!!!!  ;)
I have seen both of these movies but I prefer watching At Close Range. I purchased these movies for a family member so I am sure he will enjoy watching them. They are both good movies.
